### Description

I have a table with 12 columns defined that I am defining CSS using .scss files.
Two of the columns have CSS that is not showing up in the compiled app.

.mat-column-description and .mat-column-status-field css definitions are not showing up in rendered page
while the 10 others do show up when defining .mat-column-{columnName}

I do see the .mat-column-description and mat-column-status-field classes in the dev console, but there is no corresponding style entries.

